cordova create hello com.example.hello HelloWorld
cd hello
cordova platform add browser --save
cordova platform add android --save
cordova platform ls
cordova requirements
cordova build android
cordova build
npm install -g cordova-browser
cordova emulate browser
cordova emulate android
cordova run android


cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-dialogs      ## navigator.notification.alert()
cordova plugin ls

npm i -g cordova-jquery
cordova-jquery   ## insert jquery mobile into current project

<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />




cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-crosswalk-webview && cordova build android --info
In case of problem: Unable to load Maven meta-data from https://download.01.org/crosswalk/releases/crosswalk/android/maven2/...
 Go to platfroms/android/cordov-plugin-corsswalk-webview/*.gradle file
 Search dependencies and replace for that: dependencies{ compile 'org.xwalk:xwalk_core_library:23.53.589.4' }
 This walkaround It's not a solution. Is only to continue working.
